---
layout: layouts/base.njk
forceMode: research
title: Team
---
<section class="container page">
  <h1 class="page__title">The AIM Team</h1>
  <p class="page__lede">We are driven by curiosity, a passion for science, and a belief that doing research is rewarding and enjoyable. We treat one another with respect and honesty: we give direct feedback, we credit each other's contributions, and we have open, courageous conversations. We are committed to building a group that is diverse and inclusive, where people of every background, perspective, and experience feel they belong and can do their best work. We care about each other's wellbeing and growth, and we believe a supportive, welcoming environment is critical to doing excellent science.</p>
  <h2 class="alumni__heading">Team members</h2>
  <div class="people-grid">
    {% for person in collections.people %}
      {% if person.data.group != "alumni" %}
        <div class="person-card">
          <div class="person-card__photo">
            {% if person.data.photo %}<img src="{{ person.data.photo }}" alt="{{ person.data.name }}">{% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="person-card__name">{{ person.data.name }}</div>
          <div class="person-card__role">{{ person.data.role }}</div>
          {% if person.data.bio %}<p class="person-card__bio">{{ person.data.bio }}</p>{% endif %}
          <div class="person-card__links">
            {% if person.data.email %}<a href="mailto:{{ person.data.email }}">Email</a>{% endif %}
            {% if person.data.scholar %}<a href="{{ person.data.scholar }}">Scholar</a>{% endif %}
            {% if person.data.website %}<a href="{{ person.data.website }}">Website</a>{% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {% if album.length %}
  <div class="rule" role="presentation"></div>
  <div class="people-album">
    <h2 class="alumni__heading">Life in the group</h2>
    <div class="album-masonry" data-gallery="album">
      {% for photo in album %}
      <figure class="album-item" data-gallery-item data-src="/assets/img/album/{{ photo.src }}" data-caption="{{ photo.caption | default('') }}">
        <img src="/assets/img/album/{{ photo.src }}" alt="{{ photo.caption or 'Group photo' }}" loading="lazy">
        {% if photo.caption %}<figcaption>{{ photo.caption }}</figcaption>{% endif %}
      </figure>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lightbox" data-lightbox="album" aria-hidden="true">
    <button class="lightbox__close" data-lightbox-close aria-label="Close">×</button>
    <button class="lightbox__nav lightbox__nav--prev" data-lightbox-prev aria-label="Previous">‹</button>
    <img class="lightbox__img" data-lightbox-img src="" alt="">
    <button class="lightbox__nav lightbox__nav--next" data-lightbox-next aria-label="Next">›</button>
    <div class="lightbox__caption" data-lightbox-caption></div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if alumni.length %}
    <div class="alumni">
      <h2 class="alumni__heading">Alumni</h2>
      <ul class="alumni__list">
        {% for person in alumni %}
          <li class="alumni__item">
            <span class="alumni__name">{{ person.name | safe }}</span>
            {% if person.status %}<span class="alumni__status">{{ person.status | safe }}</span>{% endif %}
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</section>
